v0.17
-added Newton's optimizer
-added hybrid gradient descent/line search optimizer

v0.16
-added matrix utilities
-added multithreaded various imaging algorithms (resampling, transformation mapper, MPR)
-added utilities to compose/decompose affine matrices in rotation, scale, shear components
-added graph classes and basic algorithms
-added RBF deformable transformation
-added 2D/3D DDF transformation & associated resampling
-added 2D transformation estimators (similarity isotropic/anisotropic, isometry)
-added 3D distance transform
-added weighted learning for linear SVM & neural network
-added perceptron and variants
-added sampling without replacement & shuffling
-added gaussian moment and canonical representation and associated operations
-added bayesian network (linear gaussian(note:partial implementation) and table potentials)
-added bayesian inference algorithms (naive, variable elimination)
-added ML likelihood parameter estimation for bayesian network
-added normal probability density function
-improved ransac with weighted error
-improved 2D point based registration
-added simple 3D intensity based registration
-added 3D point based registration
-added new versions of adaboost
-added weak learners (neural nets, perceptron, stumps, decision trees)
-added generic weighted decision trees (discrete and continuous)
-added sparse PCA
-added quasi periodicity analysis
-added periodogram
-revisited 2D/3D transforms (resampling, MPR, mappers)

